original: Axelson, Karl Axel Olof, distriktsveterinär, Hemse, f. 13/9/05 i Stoby, Krist. 1. G. 43 m. Ulla Ringberg. Barn: Lena f. 45. — Studrex. i Örebro 26, veterinärex. 33. Resa t. Finl. 40. Konsul, i medicrstyr. 41-43, di-str :veterinär i Hemse sed. 43. FFrK-4kl m sv.
translated: Axelson, Karl Axel Olof, district veterinarian, Hemse, b. 13/9/05 in Stoby, Krist. 1. Married in 1943 to Ulla Ringberg. Children: Lena b. 1945. Studied at the University of Örebro in 1926, graduated with a degree in veterinary science in 1933. Travelled to Finland in 1940. Worked as a consul in the medical corps from 1941-1943, and has been a district veterinarian in Hemse since 1943. Awarded the Order of the Polar Star, 4th Class with a Swedish insignia.
